snippet.title: Jagged Alliance 3 | Tactical Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
In the challenging world of Jagged Alliance 3, having top-of-the-line equipment is essential for survival. Whether it's an outdoor case (100% water- and dustproof, of course), a tactical belt pouch for your gadgets, or a beautiful soundtrack to keep things atmospheric.

With the Jagged Alliance 3 Tactical Edition you can have all of this, plus a tactical belt for your pants and a Jagged Alliance branded pin as well as character cards for your favorite mercs!

The Jagged Alliance 3 Tactical Edition is available for pre-order now and will release along with the game this summer on PC.
